snippet.title: Nitro Kid - Release Date Announcement - Playtest new agents now!
snippet.description:
Nitro Kid is coming to PC on October 18!
New agents playtest starting today. Check out the video for more details.
Wishlist on Steam + Join the new Playtest:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1709050/Nitro_Kid/

Join Nitro Kid community on Discord:
https://discord.gg/MwGh8SsNKB
